                              CCNx Trace 

  -----------
  What is it?
  -----------
  The CCNx Trace is a tool with traceroute like functionality for CCNx. The CCNx
  code can be obtained at www.ccnx.org/. This tools is written for
  troubleshooting problems in CCNx environment. This tool can trace to a certain
  CCN URI, e.g, ccnx:/ndn/csu/netsec/index. This is an initial version of the
  tool and would continue to improve.

  ----------
  Components
  ----------
  The tool consists of two tools. The "trace_client" and the "trace_server".

  -------------------
  The Latest Version
  ------------------ 
  The latest version for both the client and the server is 1.0.1.
    
  -------------    
  Installation
  ------------ 
